{"tid":2515714,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"《印度平反》想分享一下我差唔多20年前去印度嘅所聞","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T17:50:50.000Z","uid":144024,"like":100,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff227ff3da90d45b06ee551d799791f4f7b9f49","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"話說睇到下面呢個 post<br />\n<br />\n屌，印度街頭美食真係世界第一。。。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2515247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2515247</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n發覺連登仔對印度嘅認知唔深同太多誤解，所以開呢個 post分享一下嗰陣我去印度嘅所見所聞。<br />\n（好耐以前喺高登都有分享過，不過今次詳細啲）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，直接開波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說我嗰陣16-17歲（差唔多20年前）當時天真爛漫嘅我對印度充滿幻想：<br />\n世界古國喎，肯定充滿歷史嘅痕跡，又想睇下生命之源⋯⋯恆河<br />\n<br />\n所以當我呀爸個印度客嫁女（會去5日4夜）請我呀爸同我呀媽去觀禮，我叫我呀爸帶埋我去。去之前，我已經做晒 research，諗定要去邊度參觀。<br />\n<br />\n臨上機前兩日，我仲預算可能唔太夠時間，所以仲叫我呀爸幫我改機票、訂酒店，我自己stay多2、3日。薑，越老越辣嘅，我呀爸嗰陣幽幽咁講：<br />\n你去到留咗2日之後仲咁諗先再講啦。<br />\n我嗰下真心嬲咗：嬲嘅係我呀爸嘅不通情，嬲嘅係我呀爸覺得我係溫室長大會頂唔順。<br />\n<br />\nAnyway，最後我地喺6月中一個陽光普照嘅天氣下出發。<br />\n<br />\n惡夢嘅開始，係由上飛機開始。<br />\n一上到機，由於班機充滿印度呀叉嘅關係加上香港天氣比較熱，就算坐嘅係 business class，成機都彌漫住一種印度香料加身體嘅酸叔味（簡單講，就係好撚柒臭）。我自問係一個文人，雖然未去到講句仆街會打冷震，但平時真心唔多講粗口。不過都要講：屌佢老味，真係好撚柒臭。<br />\n<br />\n好不容易捱過5個半鐘落機，充滿住期待咁行出機門、諗住呼吸一下古國歷史嘅氣息嘅時候。。。<br />\n迎面而黎嘅係一陣比機倉更濃烈嘅「up」味，加上微微嘅暖風帶住猛烈嘅熱氣下，肚裡面頓時感覺到胃液翻滾（簡稱「作嘔」）。之後入境、坐客㗎車去酒店嘅路上，我都一直比呢一種獨特嘅氣味熏到頭暈腦脹。<br />\n<br />\n之後嗰一日，個客好有心，搵專車車我全家去參觀下啲景點。我印象就只有：好臭、好撚臭、好撚柒臭，同好熱、好撚熱、好撚閪鳩柒熱。喺車上面有冷氣同無咁臭，但取而代之嘅係塞車塞撚到孖閪咁。你去過泰國以為泰國交通好差成日塞就見識過乜叫塞撚到仆街？<br />\n<br />\nsorry，你太天真喇，印度嘅塞車，係開外掛咁撚樣塞：係成半個鐘㗎車都郁唔到1cm嗰一種塞。去個景點講緊6-7公里外嘅，要塞成2個鐘。你可能話：屌，咁行都行到啦。啱，不過外面超過40度嘅高溫，加上嗰種臭同成街都係人，我情願塞車。<br />\n<br />\n充滿冒險精神嘅我，中途仲喺街買咗杯奶茶同街頭小食。<br />\n認真，杯奶茶無乜嘢嘅，因為夠凍，仲夠甜，算好飲添。<br />\n份街頭小食係個客嘅司機推介嘅。係一舊空心嘅炸麵包，食嗰陣就挖個洞加啲醬料。味道嘛？你幻想下食一種加牙膏嘅咖哩，再加臭臭地同苦苦地咁。好唔好味？我真係唔識欣賞囉。<br />\n<br />\n第一日其中一個 check point就係睇下生命之源嘅恆河。<br />\n唔知各位有無去過元朗國嘅B仔涼粉舊鋪食過，間嘢咪對住條渠好柒臭嘅？喺恆河嗰度附近，種臭大約係元朗國條臭渠嘅10幾20倍到。無去過元朗國？無所謂，去你而家附近一個最臭嘅公廁，對住個尿兜深呼吸，應該差唔得幾遠（點解係尿兜而唔係屎塔？因為恆河臭得黎係有種刺眼嘅「壓」味）<br />\n<br />\n喺呢一度，容許我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一下，順便表達我對我呀爸嘅尊敬：<br />\n因為佢未退休前每一年左右就要去一次印度出差，佢嗰次已經係第三、四次黎印度。果然係「強人是你，能飛天遁地」去到幾次印度，飛天遁地都係小事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（待續，下集有華麗嘅結婚場面）"},{"pid":"42d1979988d2e704dade904eb1fe7a2b217db2d2","tid":2515714,"uid":94591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7ed0568fc446578319f940a334f67d78c85c2309","tid":2515714,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"加甜thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702cd257582a33fa803d235ca17c85b318e3154e","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱 Google咗，我上面講嗰個小食係類似pani puri嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n我自問乜都敢食同接受能力好高，甚至乎去大陸3-4線城市食街邊串燒、日本納豆、長沙黑色嘅臭豆腐我都食得落<br />\n（讀書嗰陣連大佬級瑞典臭魚都食過）<br />\n<br />\n但印度呢隻「美食」真係不敢恭維<br />\n難食？唔係，但係好怪<br />\n又酸又辣又甜又苦又臭又腥又「叔」，仲有陣嘔吐物味"},{"pid":"dd61a516bbe1eebed2cb50809e9271147bf6b508","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed0568fc446578319f940a334f67d78c85c2309","tid":2515714,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"加甜thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真人真事無甜喎"},{"pid":"d940435d02161f94dbefe5e2abd20a7d7bae382f","tid":2515714,"uid":342006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"幾好睇<br />\n幾時有下集"},{"pid":"0242a7b2986ca9e212b04688a469d99e0aca57f0","tid":2515714,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"99c1fb9789953d3e436156ce73df2f06ba648c99","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"啲低賤地方有咩好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請我都唔去啦<br />\n去個越南都話有幻幻，去印度你不如插條鳩落屎坑算啦"},{"pid":"1d07121a11f38d6ad42a414b244f409adf672ef5","tid":2515714,"uid":68081,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99c1fb9789953d3e436156ce73df2f06ba648c99","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"啲低賤地方有咩好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請我都唔去啦<br />\n去個越南都話有幻幻，去印度你不如插條鳩落屎坑算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，你開post 啦一早！搶 fo 搶到嘔之餘，仲幽默風趣過樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又夠好笑好夠串嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15275994205ec4f7425be0f4d47085f316f07a4b","tid":2515714,"uid":362754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:00:27.000Z","msg":"有慘過番印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49fbe79dedd948c7fa1baf85ea85782314e09480","tid":2515714,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8679de2a0cbced8f4e0a89c94084984c6e2e8409","tid":2515714,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:01:57.000Z","msg":"即係唔係唔信你呀樓主，但20 年之印度住酒店？<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知要幾錢一晚?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續支持的！最近好有印度30cm巨根嘅出現"},{"pid":"0341888917b6b5d02d05424c2f297077dab6dd1d","tid":2515714,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係唔係唔信你呀樓主，但20 年之印度住酒店？<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知要幾錢一晚?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續支持的！最<del>近</del>好有印度30cm巨根嘅出現</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4c246482ba2d89e05f88ec1d63f447fe7c71ffd0","tid":2515714,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWfrwpFFk6poAyKgsHmzuBb4q76WNZiBsJeD9pUVZ9Z6G?filename=KRqoxvV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRqoxvV.gif&h=d29651a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5aaf6806183d74059000ab08f49b01bd8cb634e","tid":2515714,"uid":358677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"寫得幾好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ng持"},{"pid":"0b9ed7f8268fdaf3597cce8dc16410be9e607cc5","tid":2515714,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:05:52.000Z","msg":"強貼留名"},{"pid":"596c3269a267840634d1e577340562d665e986bb","tid":2515714,"uid":43013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:07:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8b01886efc57b94e5b13282aea76f006b8570963","tid":2515714,"uid":27303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"快"},{"pid":"ead49a16accec3c361119612e5ec6d9ae8e4abcd","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"Part 2:<br />\n<br />\n其實除咗pani puri ，我仲食咗幾樣街頭嘢嘅。不過都普普通通啦，不值一提。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夜晚晚餐個客安排佢其中一個下屬去招呼我地喺酒店內嘅一間西餐廳食（個客要準備第三日嫁女嘅嘢）<br />\n<br />\n嗰晚食咗乜？<br />\n我唔知喎，因為我一返到酒店就已經攬撚住個廁所潮吹咁（嗱，加甜呀嘛）噴屎。我唔係講笑，唔係普通肚痾痾水、痾爛屎嗰隻，係真係好似早幾年不幸猝死嘅潮吹女王紅音瑩（RIP）咁噴法。啲屎水係散彈式咁噴落個廁所度，中間仲要夾雜住一大堆空氣（即係放屁），搞到炸出黎嘅屎碎每一塊都係細細塊大約1cm X 1 cm。<br />\n<br />\n嗰一晚，我已經好撚想即刻返香港。<br />\n我為我幾日前話諗住自己留多2日嘅天真再耿笑多一次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二日，我已經放棄去參觀啲乜景點。<br />\n淨係喺酒店附近行下算，3餐亦喺酒店餐廳解決算。<br />\n喺附近行下嘅整體感覺係：好撚多人，邊撚度都係人。<br />\n<br />\n要記住講緊都20年前，嗰陣印度仲落後，有啲商場甚至連冷氣都唔多有。唔知有無人有戀毛癖，鍾意多毛嘅呢？ （我個人就唔太鍾意喇，比較 prefer白虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n如果你鍾意毛，去轉印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保證你 high到爆。<br />\n點解？你知啦，咁閪熱，你實著短袖、無袖衫嘅，印度男人都一樣；去到邊都邊到仆街，難免會有身體上嘅觸碰。<br />\n<br />\n印度大男人嗰一堆YY曲曲、濃厚嘅手毛，喺不經意間挑逗你嘅手臂，戀毛癖嘅你，仲唔爽到射？<br />\n<br />\n我就唔識欣賞，只係覺得好嘔心，又痴痴 lup lup 咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二晚，個客安排我全家去一間出名嘅印度餐廳去食咖哩。<br />\n當時嘅我，好天真好有冒險精神。想體驗一下用手食咖哩嘅滋味。<br />\n<br />\n魯迅好似講過：<br />\n「真正嘅美食除咗用舌頭去品嘗，仲要用身體觸覺去享受。」<br />\n<br />\n所以，就算有叉用，我都要試下。結果。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪柒撚到起水囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一來我又無用開手食飯，搞到一獲泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺試咗2分鐘後，都係 spoon please <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，平心而論，嗰餐咖哩係好食嘅，亦係成個旅程我第二享受嘅嘢黎（第一開心我之後會講到嘅）<br />\n尤其係咖哩芝士 paneer，真心好食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只不過，當晚一樣係噴撚晒去廁所度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家實睇過有錢印度佬嫁女有幾開心有幾熱鬧㗎嘛？<br />\n咁事實係點呢？<br />\n<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"28c09ad6a1fe4e34ed3626da57871b7d15ecc229","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d940435d02161f94dbefe5e2abd20a7d7bae382f","tid":2515714,"uid":342006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"幾好睇<br />\n幾時有下集"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:26:22.000Z","msg":"有喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf608d58deade80fef95fc0fcc96e384c7c694b8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"99c1fb9789953d3e436156ce73df2f06ba648c99","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"啲低賤地方有咩好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請我都唔去啦<br />\n去個越南都話有幻幻，去印度你不如插條鳩落屎坑算啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"20年前呀，資訊邊有咁發達<br />\n係聽過慘過返印度，但無諗過真係咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我17-18歲嗰陣有一段時間好迷呢一啲歷史古國，覺得好神秘好特別。而家？你請我都唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59093efa6d40ec30101c7bd0ce021510ee3fe4f","tid":2515714,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865936b4aeadb7dd47b998aa7cb6a6da066f714f","tid":2515714,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"等睇相"},{"pid":"28a8a346fd5b4814716df5daa158664d2aa5e60f","tid":2515714,"uid":384679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf608d58deade80fef95fc0fcc96e384c7c694b8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"99c1fb9789953d3e436156ce73df2f06ba648c99","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"啲低賤地方有咩好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請我都唔去啦<br />\n去個越南都話有幻幻，去印度你不如插條鳩落屎坑算啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"20年前呀，資訊邊有咁發達<br />\n係聽過慘過返印度，但無諗過真係咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我17-18歲嗰陣有一段時間好迷呢一啲歷史古國，覺得好神秘好特別。而家？你請我都唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"就好似鬼佬好迷華夏古國 然後望到而家嘅支共國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689e9957f586fedc50852f701d64d8bd5064ee04","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf608d58deade80fef95fc0fcc96e384c7c694b8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"99c1fb9789953d3e436156ce73df2f06ba648c99","tid":2515714,"uid":33874,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"啲低賤地方有咩好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請我都唔去啦<br />\n去個越南都話有幻幻，去印度你不如插條鳩落屎坑算啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"20年前呀，資訊邊有咁發達<br />\n係聽過慘過返印度，但無諗過真係咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我17-18歲嗰陣有一段時間好迷呢一啲歷史古國，覺得好神秘好特別。而家？你請我都唔撚去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"20年前啲呀差已經好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭丁丁見到我寧願唔坐落樓下迫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73dcad6eceb2fbd1c00c89b6da5666dc5bd009c","tid":2515714,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"高質屎尿post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b815d1a90838c385c65f77532a4637eb0806f1e9","tid":2515714,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1c2fbbd5c53ac8e4553f48eb2fe60074ba3bbc09","tid":2515714,"uid":261522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幾年之前去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇咁差"},{"pid":"6b29d1a16bcfd239515368d8c56a9c8b4dee4057","tid":2515714,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:44:38.000Z","msg":"連google map grab 都冇 想像唔到點去<br />\n不過果時D人可能冇咁仆街"},{"pid":"b953fd7c16691990a972dbf99405401ccd58e872","tid":2515714,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"感覺上印度尚算安全 冇比人搶野<br />\n去南美中美比人搵刀仔行頸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4426098193ade15529bdf934d267a371fe896a2f","tid":2515714,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:57:46.000Z","msg":"食完飯好出文啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9946a1c7910ad52695e25d9f83b365fca70f1d","tid":2515714,"uid":121238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:09:00.000Z","msg":"出文啦"},{"pid":"940cd6d7f68996b8c64a2562acf5612525ff6372","tid":2515714,"uid":15622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />印度啲牛係咪多過新界"},{"pid":"13fcfa64adaf792f6f4fe1b59832cfb0a68d4983","tid":2515714,"uid":296991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:14:12.000Z","msg":"叫你條女自己去多幾次試試"},{"pid":"1d0d0a66905db51f05209537c980448182bb4e2d","tid":2515714,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:18:35.000Z","msg":"之前旅遊台有個印度遊記寫得好正<br />\n<br />\n結局仲好凄美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc70d03a30252af1e35974e864f03b9747e9e6de","tid":2515714,"uid":8681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"屎既國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a572f75f0514b9c0818b64576e796ed0b7eae69c","tid":2515714,"uid":100365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n有生之年點都會去一次印度見識下"},{"pid":"54b02fc3074d2129c4f5532ca9dc500337e53939","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"Part 3:<br />\n<br />\n第三日，去我呀爸個客嘅婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n因為已過咗兩日，基本上個人已經習慣咗嗰陣印度味（即係嗰陣酸酸叔叔咸咸臭臭嘅呀叉味）。雖然未去到免疫，但只要唔係去到特別臭嘅地方，其實都無乜反應。<br />\n<br />\n咁婚禮雖然係喺半室外（因為太多賓客，所以招待賓客嘅地方係室外黎，而結婚搞啲乜鳩儀式就由雙方家長同親戚走去室內。但我真係屌佢老味，夏天搞室外結婚）會有好多大大隻嘅汗臭印度佬（or 婆）<br />\n但婚禮現場實有好多花圈嗰啲，我對花香好有信心，會掩蓋得住汗臭嘅侵略。<br />\n<br />\n我再講一次，我當年真係好傻好天真，絕對天真過天真嬌。<br />\n無論幾多鮮花都好，都唔會抵抗得住差唔多成千個大汗淋漓嘅賓客。我當一半係男人，有80%係呀叉，即係有400個著suit嘅汗臭點。仲有唔同小組好耐無見要攬下跳下增加活動量兼促進排汗量，你可想而知有幾臭。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪嘅係，呀叉可能聞慣恆河，佢地無人覺得臭㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班大汗呀叉，有啲直頭大汗到suit都濕鳩埋。<br />\n<br />\n成個婚禮，我已經唔記得點捱過。<br />\n我淨係知我一直都好想嘔好唔舒服好熱好熱好撚熱。<br />\n香港濕熱第一難捱？<br />\n成都火爐天下最熱？<br />\nSorry，你問過印度臭熱未？<br />\n熱量將臭味蒸發再由你吸入令到你身體熱之餘仲反胃兩重鋏型攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺宴會現場，我睇住我呀爸就算熱到孖閪咁都一樣保持專業咁去應酬，我親眼睇到咩嘢係撐起頭家嘅大樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（待續，下集 final，講回程。以為返到香港就無事？恐怖片隻鬼臨尾都嚇多你一齋啦）"},{"pid":"dcbe482d4a0d67ab314e38836451d44b3b6e1a62","tid":2515714,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b02fc3074d2129c4f5532ca9dc500337e53939","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"Part 3:<br />\n<br />\n第三日，去我呀爸個客嘅婚禮。<br />\n<br />\n因為已過咗兩日，基本上個人已經習慣咗嗰陣印度味（即係嗰陣酸酸叔叔咸咸臭臭嘅呀叉味）。雖然未去到免疫，但只要唔係去到特別臭嘅地方，其實都無乜反應。<br />\n<br />\n咁婚禮雖然係喺半室外（因為太多賓客，所以招待賓客嘅地方係室外黎，而結婚搞啲乜鳩儀式就由雙方家長同親戚走去室內。但我真係屌佢老味，夏天搞室外結婚）會有好多大大隻嘅汗臭印度佬（or 婆）<br />\n但婚禮現場實有好多花圈嗰啲，我對花香好有信心，會掩蓋得住汗臭嘅侵略。<br />\n<br />\n我再講一次，我當年真係好傻好天真，絕對天真過天真嬌。<br />\n無論幾多鮮花都好，都唔會抵抗得住差唔多成千個大汗淋漓嘅賓客。我當一半係男人，有80%係呀叉，即係有400個著suit嘅汗臭點。仲有唔同小組好耐無見要攬下跳下增加活動量兼促進排汗量，你可想而知有幾臭。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪嘅係，呀叉可能聞慣恆河，佢地無人覺得臭㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班大汗呀叉，有啲直頭大汗到suit都濕鳩埋。<br />\n<br />\n成個婚禮，我已經唔記得點捱過。<br />\n我淨係知我一直都好想嘔好唔舒服好熱好熱好撚熱。<br />\n香港濕熱第一難捱？<br />\n成都火爐天下最熱？<br />\nSorry，你問過印度臭熱未？<br />\n熱量將臭味蒸發再由你吸入令到你身體熱之餘仲反胃兩重鋏型攻勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺宴會現場，我睇住我呀爸就算熱到孖閪咁都一樣保持專業咁去應酬，我親眼睇到咩嘢係撐起頭家嘅大樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（待續，下集 final，講回程。以為返到香港就無事？恐怖片隻鬼臨尾都嚇多你一齋啦）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"快啦"},{"pid":"6c6fffd4afd112c8564dd2b659328c72c42fcc1d","tid":2515714,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你依家覺得有咩係慘過翻印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0035c00642a6f0d2fbf135c980e4aaa118c0d3d8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"6c6fffd4afd112c8564dd2b659328c72c42fcc1d","tid":2515714,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你依家覺得有咩係慘過翻印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"翻印度2次"},{"pid":"129b29f7f56647796ffb7710b006bf8a643c2bc7","tid":2515714,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"平反d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />20年前咁耐都唔同"},{"pid":"91cbb90b8e672ccd921a9ccda162082fdb99642c","tid":2515714,"uid":172520,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"強貼劉明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主文筆好撚正<br />\n睇文字真係好似聞到氣味咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d1c261d2b413ad6942c056569e8e675fc87df8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"Part 4 - final <br />\n<br />\n大家有無行過啲毒撚場見到啲咸碟鋪嘅poster 好好好吸引之後抄低個番號，打算翻屋企上avgle 搵套嘢出黎打個靚J。<br />\n<br />\n之不過唔喺翻屋企嗰程車就諗翻起之前好幾次發生過一樣嘅事情，但結果係封殺而失望，最後都係J翻套J咗好多次嘅蒼井空。嗰一刻，想J新嘢嘅心情就冷卻咗，頓時發現習慣嘅美好：新嘢雖然有新鮮感，但始終好多時最後都係驚嚇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對我黎講，印度就係嗰一套行街望到好正嗰套AV，充滿期待。去之前我知會好污糟、好多人，但心諗歷史大國喎，差極睇遺跡都夠好啦。<br />\n<br />\n正如個AV封面係美女教師迫姦、條女又靚又大波，你會預期差極有個限度啦。點知一睇，條女樣衰不突止，仲要煙屎牙兼死魚格，最大獲係扮男學生嗰個係東尼大木，屌你老味，個學生望落仲仲老過個老師一截<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情況唔同嘅係，AV始終係AV，要硬J都劣得落。<br />\n但印度根本就係AV嘅封面，入面原來係女教師迫鳩啲學生係hehe，仲要玩屎玩尿嗰隻。<br />\n<br />\n嗰5日，我真心體驗到咩叫「慘過翻印度」。我再重申一次，我算係有啲教養，平時真係唔會講太多粗口嘅，但我估真係無乜嘢係會慘撚過翻印度囉。<br />\n<br />\n回程，我懷住興奮嘅心情坐個客嘅車去機場，又塞撚到冚家鏟、㗎車都有陣呀叉味、個肚又好似搞搞地等等最後嘅閪嘢我已經唔再介意，因為我嗰晚就可以翻屋企，呼吸住清新嘅空氣J我套蒼井空。<br />\n<br />\n喺機場，臨上機前，個客送咗一大盒芒果比我地。<br />\n印度送芒果係好好好得體嘅禮儀黎（好似韓國人送韓牛咁）<br />\n<br />\n翻到香港屋企，喺我又潮吹轟炸完個廁所、沖咗個大半粒鐘嘅涼去洗晒身上沾染嘅呀叉味之後，我呀爸叫我幫手撬開個木箱食芒果。<br />\n<br />\n我本身好鍾意食芒果嘅，我諗住用呢兩隻芒果去洗個塵、順便當係比啲掌聲自己去捱過嗰5日嘅印度之旅。<br />\n<br />\n點知一撬開個木箱，嗰下真係要借用周星星馳套戲嘅一幕：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUJ3umYUWMjbstujdbHdswLhBSKskfjqkReRn4izY8rrT?filename=tDqLMPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDqLMPO.jpg&h=515f282f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屌佢老味，連啲芒果都有嗰陣呀叉味。。。"},{"pid":"4d07b87fc6050e6e05004f6820f27a622f363e1d","tid":2515714,"uid":261639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"星期日旺角天橋既味道"},{"pid":"bc7cbe38a87a0c95e0ce90bbf4e07af3af740ede","tid":2515714,"uid":1252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"樓主寫得幾好，搭車睇到笑到我gapgap 聲"},{"pid":"1557ab0a5094c390964edaae479d2c49cca8d292","tid":2515714,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:19:28.000Z","msg":"芒果個位笑到我仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8155d7dcbc0cb89281af644298961651d98697fb","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"129b29f7f56647796ffb7710b006bf8a643c2bc7","tid":2515714,"uid":17420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"平反d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />20年前咁耐都唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:21:39.000Z","msg":"連登仔會覺得印度好落後，好污糟<br />\n<br />\n我想替印度平反一下：根本就比你想像中差十幾廿倍有多<br />\n慘過翻印度呢一句形容詞實在太睇少佢喇<br />\n<br />\n你話我馬後炮啦，但上年武肺印度得嗰十幾萬 case根本係無撚可能。以印度咁撚污糟，唔中夠幾千萬、甚至過億根本就唔撚係印度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有連登仔會話：<br />\n挑，大陸啲5-6線城市咪一鳩樣，分分鐘仲閪啦<br />\n<br />\n我會話你知，根本無撚得比。<br />\n<br />\n因工作關係，我試過要飛上海，但中間預上台風迫降江西南昌，國航安排夜晚入住間旅館我一入門見到兩隻老鼠望住我添。又去過昆明，為咗去睇紅土地住啲狂偏僻嘅酒店。<br />\n大陸係唔乾淨，會污糟，但個規模同印度真係差幾條街。<br />\n大陸去個廁所，最差咪地下有屎有尿。印度嘅公廁，你係會見到有呀叉等唔到廁格就咁喺角落痾緊屎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有，印度呀叉痾完屎尿，目測有8成人係直接走，唔撚洗手嘅，所以街邊小食有錢味？你食真啲，喺陣銀紙、乳酪、masala、呀叉味嘅掩蓋下，仲有鳩屎味。<br />\n<br />\n印度5星酒店都靚㗎，但我情願去20次大陸4-5線城市都唔會去多一次印度。"},{"pid":"78fd43f6f973a18a48b075c0f0387aa135ab3bc8","tid":2515714,"uid":144024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d07b87fc6050e6e05004f6820f27a622f363e1d","tid":2515714,"uid":261639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:11:19.000Z","msg":"星期日旺角天橋既味道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"起碼再濃縮多20倍"},{"pid":"50653150640af05988c0360f9878d78b720d758e","tid":2515714,"uid":385190,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"衰鬼又寫得幾盞鬼wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}